# Power Grid Cascade Failure Simulator

## 1. Goal Description
Create an entirely independent simulation module (`power_simulation.py`) to model cascading failures in the Bengaluru power grid. The simulator will use electrical flow redistribution and rule-based physics, detecting overloaded transformers, transmission trips, voltage collapse, and grid islanding. It will operate as a standalone Flask service on port `5002`.

## 2. User Review Required
